_sText:
Hello people..
==============
The time has come, my second version of the map is public. Middle of the woods you will find a small fortress, which was occupied by terrorists. As a counter-terrorist, it is your task to liberate the fortress of the terrorists. In the castle to shore radio, there is a very small lake. You'll find four ways into the castle. The main entrance with its huge gates and three ways to climb into the castle.
